name: Tribe Elders ~ Nana Uwimana
description:
Cocao skin soft and playful. Eyes that dart gently here and then. She sees everything. Eyes open and closed.

Her hair tinged with platinum flecks. The Sun bounces kindly from her hair which appear as millions of long flowing antennae.

The Earth Loves her presence and the Tribe does too. Her compassion is endless. Wisdom great and Divinity strong.

If She calls. You hear.
When She speaks. You listen.

God has his hands on Nana and she opens her arms to You.
